videos.description: Kenneth Walker returns the opening kickoff 75 yards to the house to give Michigan State an early 7-0 lead over Northwestern.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kenneth Walker III runs in 75-yard kickoff TD) 2021/09/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kenneth Walker III runs in 75-yard kickoff TD

videos.description: Kenneth Walker takes the handoff and changes direction to elude the defense and score a short 3-yard touchdown for Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kenneth Walker shifts directions to score short TD) 2021/09/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kenneth Walker shifts directions to score short TD

videos.description: Michigan State pushes their lead to 21-0 over Northwestern as Payton Thorn completes a pass to Jordon Simmons who travels 14 yards to reach pay dirt.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Payton Thorne finds Jordon Simmons for 14-yard TD) 2021/09/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Payton Thorne finds Jordon Simmons for 14-yard TD

videos.description: Northwestern gets on the board at the end of the second quarter as Hunter Johnson finds Trey Pugh in the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hunter Johnson connects with Trey Pugh for Northwestern TD) 2021/09/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hunter Johnson connects with Trey Pugh for Northwestern TD

videos.description: Kenneth Walker takes the handoff, gets to the outside and dives for the pylon to score his third touchdown of the game and gives Michigan State a 28-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kenneth Walker dives to score his 3rd TD of the game) 2021/09/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kenneth Walker dives to score his 3rd TD of the game

videos.description: Northwestern cuts the Michigan State lead to 28-14 as Hunter Johnson darts a pass to Trey Pugh for the 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Trey Pugh reels in his 2nd TD reception of the game) 2021/09/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trey Pugh reels in his 2nd TD reception of the game

videos.description: Hunter Johnson darts a quick pass to Stephon Robinson who slides to make a a14-yard touchdown reception for Northwestern.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stephon Robinson Jr. makes 14-yard TD grab) 2021/09/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stephon Robinson Jr. makes 14-yard TD grab

videos.description: Kenneth Walker gets the handoff and navigates his way through traffic to dive into the end zone and score his fourth touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kenneth Walker dives to score his 4th touchdown of the game) 2021/09/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kenneth Walker dives to score his 4th touchdown of the game

videos.description: Kenneth Walker has a night to remember as he racks up four touchdowns and 264 yards in Michigan State's 38-21 win over Northwestern.
